  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AMEND CHAPTER 913, LOCAL AND PRIVATE LAWS OF 2022, BY EXTENDING THE DATE OF REPEAL FROM JULY 1, 2022, TO JULY 1, 2030, ON THE PROVISIONS OF LAW THAT AUTHORIZES THE GOVERNING AUTHORITIES OF THE TOWN OF RALEIGH, MISSISSIPPI, TO LEVY A 2% TAX UPON THE GROSS PROCEEDS OF SALES OF RESTAURANTS FOR THE PURPOSE OF PROVIDING FUNDS TO PROMOTE TOURISM AND PARKS AND RECREATION WITHIN THE TOWN; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
  },
